title: Public invited to join consultation sessions on District Health Centre in Kwai Tsing District
content_text: Details are as follows: Date: July 28 (Saturday) Time: 2pm to 5pm Venue: Lai King Community Hall, 205 Lai King Hill Road, Kwai Chung, New Territories (MTR Lai King Station, Exit A3) Date: August 4 (Saturday) Time: 2pm to 5pm Venue: CNEC Ta Tung School, 103 Kwai Hing Road, Kwai Chung, New Territories (MTR Kwai Hing Station, Exit A) People who would like to attend the consultation sessions should complete the reply slip at the

Exit A) People who would like to attend the consultation sessions should complete the reply slip at the FHB's website (www.fhb.gov.hk/en/press_and_publications/otherinfo/180700_dhc/index_kt.html) and return the slip by email (

(kwtdcadm@kwtdc.had.gov.hk), by fax (2425 4299) or by post to 10/F, Kwai Hing Government Offices Building, 166-174 Hing Fong Road, Kwai Chung, New Territories (Attn: EO(SPS)/K&T). Participants may also call 3509 7934 for seat reservation or enquiries. Seats will be allocated on a first-come, first-served
for seat reservation or enquiries. Seats will be allocated on a first-come, first-served basis.  Walk-in registrations will be accepted when there are vacant seats on the spot.
